163
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:53,700
An obsession, a thought,
a fleeting life.

164
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:56,420
A sorrow, a joy, and a regret.

165
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,180
Life is like a dream.

166
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:08,420
How long can one enjoy happiness?

167
00:11:09,180 --> 00:11:10,260
Only the beauty

168
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:12,020
