169
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:16,500
Congratulations, sir.

170
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:19,500
The prize is yours now.

171
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:24,540
Impressive.

172
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,420
May you always

173
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:33,100
witness a full moon
on every Mid-Autumn Festival.

174
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,220
Here's for you.

175
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:41,340
I wish you a great reunion feast

176
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:42,740
under the moonlight every year.

177
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:46,420
Buhan,

178
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:48,220
